Chinese: 在当今市场中非常普遍的工具，
它已将数以百万计的人

English: So these tools basically are tools to find and source people.
Some of the tools that are very prevalent in today's market, one of my absolute favorites is LinkedIn.
It has connected millions upon millions of people throughout various countries in technology.
